<A>__{the couple who sleep on the fire escape. the increasing rain cause them to hastily gather their things to retreat inside. the man, hurriedly untying the alarm clock from the railing of the fire escape, lets it slip through his fingers. as if falls to the garden below, the camera fans swiftly down with it. when the clock hits the ground, the alarm goes off sending a shrill sound through the neighborhood.}
